To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private DoubleExponentialMovingAverage _dema;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_dema = DEMA(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_dema.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "doubleexponentialmovingaverage", _dema.Current.Value);
}
